<li>Spear, Percival. 1958. "Britain's Transfer of Power in India." <i>Pacific Affairs</i>, 31(2):173-180.</li>
<li>Talbot, Ian. 1994. "Planning for Pakistan: The Planning Committee of the All-India Muslim League, 1943-46". <i>Modern Asian Studies</i>, 28(4):875-889.</li>
<li>Visaria, Pravin M. 1969. "Migration Between India and Pakistan, 1951-61" <i>Demography</i>, 6(3):323-334.</li>
</ul>
